lead_paragraph: Ellen Port won her third U.S. Senior Women's Amateur title and seventh USGA championship Thursday, beating Andrea Kraus 3 and 2 at Wellesley Country Club.

headline.print_headline: Ellen Port Wins Third US Senior Women's Amateur
